{"tid":1359652,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有去發夢嘅四眼仔入黎！","createTime":"2019-07-24T07:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T08:32:21.000Z","uid":264538,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9859801441013c7c9db05cb0228d2ff81b31f465","tid":1359652,"uid":264538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:37:16.000Z","msg":"咁多位如果你地有食過催淚彈<br />\n你地應該知道對眼係有幾難受<br />\n<br />\n除左換過款眼罩之外<br />\n四眼仔有個好嚴重嘅問題就係<br />\n鏡框嘅腳會令到眼罩與面部之間有空隙<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點</span></span><br />\n相信咁多位四眼清都有番幾副舊眼鏡<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拆左鏡框果兩隻腳佢</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bOeK1br.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbOeK1br.png&h=8124e0a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果螺絲批頭唔夠細<br />\n可以用橡筋/氣球墊低<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mrWYmbu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmrWYmbu.png&h=3080634f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拆完將眼鏡放入眼罩</span></span><br />\n用膠紙或者更好嘅方法固定佢啦<br />\n小弟呢副就岩岩好唔需要固定<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uybmiWe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuybmiWe.png&h=876d93f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">希望有幫到咁多位四眼清</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果有更好嘅方法請指教</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TShD5GY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTShD5GY.png&h=944b1c3b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N3wJxmZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN3wJxmZ.png&h=f0d3fad7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4bc4aa92e0a9d3ae1e429405f7583247bb0c39b","tid":1359652,"uid":264538,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:39:42.000Z","msg":"推比所四眼仔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac173350ad2517220644a535b68b9a17a4acc3f8","tid":1359652,"uid":277186,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:42:07.000Z","msg":"一定好暈囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0a023721e08c013b71e7ccb26f5ffa2456d68b","tid":1359652,"uid":264538,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ac173350ad2517220644a535b68b9a17a4acc3f8","tid":1359652,"uid":277186,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:42:07.000Z","msg":"一定好暈囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:42:53.000Z","msg":"試過，還可以算頂得順嘅<br />\n總好過食煙"},{"pid":"859ec1171d5c9ddca4b92639db168cf17f16bc8d","tid":1359652,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:43:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a07f005da309ed69a5a3d178e4542753390f44c","tid":1359652,"uid":275865,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:43:31.000Z","msg":"有度數泳鏡"},{"pid":"6f17c8983f38857e7a493e5fd0e140467ebcf807","tid":1359652,"uid":34478,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:43:59.000Z","msg":"買副有度數嘅泳鏡咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89